a le Fevre ||\n|-\n| 2013 || ''[[For Those in Peril (2013 film)|For Those in Peril]]'' || Cathy ||\n|-\n| 2014 || ''Soror'' || Amanda || Short\n|-\n| 2014 || ''[[Catch Me Daddy]]'' || ||\n|-\n| 2015 || ''[[The Witch (2015 film)|The Witch]]'' || Katherine ||\n|-\n| 2015 || ''Couple in a Hole'' || Karen ||\n|-\n| 2015 || ''Gracie'' || Mary || Short\n|-\n| 2016 || ''[[Prevenge]]'' || Ella ||\n|-\n| 2017 || ''[[Star Wars: The Last Jedi|Star Wars VIII : The Last Jedi]]'' || First Order Officer ||\n|-\n| 2018 || ''[[Tell It to the Bees]]'' || Pam Kranmer ||\n|-\n| 2019 || ''[[Balance, Not Symmetry]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.screendaily.com/news/laura-harrier-bria-vinaite-lily-newmark-board-balance-not-symmetry-with-biffy-clyro-exclusive/5133310.article|title=Laura Harrier, Bria Vinaite, Lily Newmark board 'Balance, Not Symmetry' with Biffy Clyro (exclusive)|website=Screen International|first=Tom|last=Grater|date=October 5, 2018|accessdate=December 30, 2018}}</ref> || Mary Walker ||\n|-\n| 2020 || ''[[The Green Knight (film)|The Green Knight]]'' || || Post-production\n|}\n\n===Video Game===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year !! Title !! Role\n|-\n| 2020 || ''The Complex'' || \n|}\n\n== Awards and nominations ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Award\n! Work\n! Result\n|-\n| 2000\n| [[BAFTA Scotland|British Academy Scotland Award]] Best Television Performance\n| ''[[Tinsel Town]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| 2006\n|  British Academy Scotland Award Best Actress in a Scottish Film\n| ''[[Red Road (film)|Red Road]]''\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| 2006\n| [[British Independent Film Award]] for [[BIFA Award for Best Performance by an Actress in a British Independent Film|Best Actress in a British Independent Film]]\n| ''Red Road''\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| 2006\n| [[Festival du nouveau cin\u00e9ma|Montreal Festival of New Cinema]] Acting Award for Best Actress\n| ''Red Road''\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| 2007\n| [[London Film Critics' Circle]] Award for [[London Film Critics Circle Awards 2006#