ilies of John Chrysostom\",(John Henry Parker, trans.), London. J. Rivington, 1841, p. 44-52]</ref>\n<ref name=\"Elvira\">[http://faculty.cua.edu/pennington/Canon%20Law/ElviraCanons.htm Canon 71] {{webarchive|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AS7rgB7f?url=http://faculty.cua.edu/pennington/canon%20Law/ElviraCanons.htm |date= 5 September 2012}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"ReferenceB\">Pierre Player (editor), ''Book of Gomorrah: Eleventh century treatise against clerical homosexual practices'', Wilfrid Laurier University Press, 1982, notes</ref>\n<ref name=\"Pierre J. Payer 1982 p. 29\">[http://www.fordham.edu/halsall/source/homo-damian1.asp Pierre J. Payer, ''Book of Gomorrah'' (Wilfrid Laurier University Press, 1982), p. 29]</ref>\n<ref name=\"autogenerated1998\">Rictor Norton, ''My Dear Boy: Gay love letters through the centuries'', Leyland, 1998</ref>\n<ref name=\"fone\">{{cite book |last1=Fone |first1=Byrne |title=Homophobia: A History |date=2001 |publisher=Macmillan |isbn=978-0-312-42030-7 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=gL_nAQGxI_IC |language=en}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"SBS\">\"Bologna, parts of Portugal and other regions embracing Roman civic law prescribed death by fire for convicted sodomites\" - [https://books.google.com/books?id=JpjBdA7iFokC&pg=PT79 Kim M. Phillips, Barry Reay, ''Sex Before Sexuality: A Premodern History''] (John Wiley & Sons 2013 {{ISBN|978-0-74563726-6}})</ref>\n<ref name=\"HaggertyGeorge\">Haggerty, George E. (2000). [https://books.google.com/books?id=L9Mj7oHEwVoC&pg=PA471 Gay histories and cultures: an encyclopedia.] Taylor & Francis, pp. 470-471</ref>\n<ref name=\"Perez\">[https://books.google.com/books?id=5B3S6zOCpIEC&pg=PA92&dq=P%C3%A9rez+%22where+sodomy%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=Va2gUuapMNGIhQfuioGICQ&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=P%C3%A9rez%20%22where%20sodomy%22&f=false Joseph P\u00e9rez, ''The Spanish Inquisition''] (Profile Books 2006 {{ISBN|978-1-86197622-2}}), pp. 91-92</ref>\n<ref name=\"buttigieg\">{{cite book|last=Buttigieg|first=Emanuel|date=20