07.pdf|date=2007|volume=14|page=448}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"kWGvJ\">[https://archive.org/stream/compendiumtheolo00gabr#page/264/mode/2up/search/%22crimen+pessimum%22 Gabriel de Varceno, ''Compendium theologiae moralis\" (Marietti, Turin 1873), p. 264]</ref>\n<ref name=\"X1R1W\">[https://books.google.com/books?id=izRAAAAAcAAJ&pg=PA52&dq=%22crimen+pessimum%22+theologia&hl=en&sa=X&ei=aCOsU4DcB6_Q7AbegYHYDg&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=%22crimen%20pessimum%22%20theologia&f=false Maurus Hagel, ''Demonstratio Religionis Christianae Catholicae'' (Vienna, 1831), p. 52]</ref>\n<ref name=\"vpLfB\">For instance in documents of [https://books.google.com/books?id=6FTcpQXsQRMC&pg=PA377&dq=%22crimen+pessimum%22%7C&hl=en&sa=X&ei=83tyUsKXHsa47QbKx4HwCg&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=%22crimen%20pessimum%22%7C&f=false 1390], [https://books.google.com/books?id=kONiZS-QJp4C&pg=PA133&dq=%22crimen+pessimum%22%7C&hl=en&sa=X&ei=qnhyUu-AG6yI7Abt_4DgDg&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=%22crimen%20pessimum%22%7C&f=false 1525], [https://books.google.com/books?id=0borAAAAMAAJ&pg=PA37&dq=%22crimen+pessimum%22%7C&hl=en&sa=X&ei=qnhyUu-AG6yI7Abt_4DgDg&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=%22crimen%20pessimum%22%7C&f=false 1591], [https://books.google.com/books?id=GSVUNxerfbYC&pg=RA1-PA112&dq=%22crimen+pessimum%22%7C&hl=en&sa=X&ei=83tyUsKXHsa47QbKx4HwCg&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=%22crimen%20pessimum%22%7C&f=false 1622], [https://books.google.com/books?id=fnLQ4hmhYOsC&pg=PA272&dq=%22crimen+pessimum%22%7C&hl=en&sa=X&ei=qnhyUu-AG6yI7Abt_4DgDg&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=%22crimen%20pessimum%22%7C&f=false 1851]</ref>\n<ref name=\"UhSn4\">[https://books.google.com/books?id=ZYkUAAAAIAAJ&q=%22crimen+pessimum%22%7C&dq=%22crimen+pessimum%22%7C&hl=en&sa=X&ei=83tyUsKXHsa47QbKx4HwCg&redir_esc=y Theological Studies, vol. 9 (1948), p. 630]; [https://books.google.com/books?id=oPnP4edaOrUC&pg=PA9&dq=%22crimen+pessimum%22%7C&hl=en&sa=X&ei=83tyUsKXHsa47QbKx4HwCg&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=%22crimen%20pessimum%22%7C&f=false Document of the Holy Office in 1962]; [